==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transfluent
<hw>Trans"flu*ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>trans-</ets> + <ets>fluent</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Flowing
or running across or through; <as>as, a <ex>transfluent</ex>
stream</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>Passing or flowing through a
bridge; -- said of water.</def> <rj><au>Wright.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Transflux</ent>⟦br⟧
